<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="globals.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="navbar.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="index.css" />
    <title>Stacks of Wax</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("./partials/navbar") %>

    <div class="flex-container">
      <main class="main">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1662354333661-1c18107484b9?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80" alt="" class="banner-image">
        <header class="page-header">
          <% if (user) { %>
          <h2 class="welcome-header"><%= user.firstName %>'s Dashboard</h2>
          <hr/>
          <% } else { %>
          <h2 class="welcome-header">What is Stacks of Wax?</h2>
          <p class="header-text">
            Whether you're a musician looking to showcase your talents or a
            music lover in search of your next favorite track, Stacks Of Wax is
            the perfect pplatform for you to connect with like-minded individuals
            and explore the world of music. With our user-friendly interface and
            vast collection of songs, you can easily create collections, share
            your favorite tracks with friends, and discover new music that
            speaks to your soul. So sit back, relax, and let the music take you
            on a journey.
          </p>
          <hr/>
          <h3>So how does it work?</h3>
          <p class="header-text">
            Stacks Of Wax is an open community! That means <b>anybody</b> can
            browse our catalogue of vinyls, artists, and check out our member's
            profiles, no membership required!
          </p>
          <hr/>
          <h3>How can I share my records with the world?</h3>
          <p class="header-text">
            If you want to contribute to the Stacks Of Wax community, you'll
            need to <a href="/register">set up a FREE account!</a> Creating an
            account is super fast and easy, and once you're registered you'll
            have full access to all of the features on the site!
          </p>
          <hr/>
          <h3>Members can:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Customise their own profile</li>
            <li>Add records to our catalogue</li>
            <li>Create collections to share with the world</li>
            <li>Like, comment and review other member's collections</li>
          </ul>
          <% } %>
          <div class="card-grid">
            <% if (user) { %>
              <div class="card">
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="card blocked">
              <% } %>
              <div class="card-header">
                <img
                  class="card-image"
                  src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1668494833871-50d2874c9189?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1166&q=80"
                  alt=""
                />
              </div>
              <div class="card-body">
                Found a hidden gem? Share it with the world!
              </div>
              <div class="card-footer">
                <% if (user) { %>
                  <button class="btn">Add Vinyl</button>
                <% } else { %>
                  <button class="btn">Add Vinyl (Members Only)</button>
                  <% } %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <% if (user) { %>
              <div class="card">
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="card blocked">
              <% } %>
              <div class="card-header">
                <img
                  class="card-image"
                  src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1488841714725-bb4c32d1ac94?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1130&q=80"
                  alt=""
                />
              </div>
              <div class="card-body">
                  Mix and Match your favourite records to create something unique!   
              </div>
              <div class="card-footer">
                <% if (user) { %>
                  <button class="btn">Create a Collection</button>
                <% } else { %>
                  <button class="btn">Create Collection (Members Only)</button>
                  <% } %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <img
                  class="card-image"
                  src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607749111659-e1c8e05f5f24?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8M3x8ZnJpZW5kc3xlbnwwfHwwfHw%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=60"
                  alt=""
                />
              </div>
              <div class="card-body">
                Check out our member profiles and see what people are sharing!
              </div>
              <div class="card-footer">
                <button class="btn">Member Profiles</button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <img
                  class="card-image"
                  src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605722243979-fe0be8158232?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80"
                  alt=""
                />
              </div>
              <div class="card-body">
                From Bob Marley to Black Sabbath, you'll find them all here!
              </div>
              <div class="card-footer">
                <button class="btn">Browse Artists</button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <img
                  class="card-image"
                  src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605055510925-4c9626126167?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=435&q=80"
                  alt=""
                />
              </div>
              <div class="card-body">
                Our members have curated collections to suit any taste, check them
                out here!
              </div>
              <div class="card-footer">
                <button class="btn">Browse Collections</button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <img
                  class="card-image"
                  src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599663253408-ddd8dadac635?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1169&q=80"
                  alt=""
                />
              </div>
              <div class="card-body">
                Whether its hip-hop or heavy metal,
                we guarantee you'll find it here!
              </div>
              <div class="card-footer">
                <button class="btn">Browse Genres</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </main>
      </div>
        </header>

        
  </body>
  <script src="navbar.js"></script>
</html>
